[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1216330","time":"2017-2-28 08:42","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"(V1046-R MAHORO)","message":"塚简化成冢了啊。","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/78/267845.jpg","floor":"#2-1","id":"1216332","time":"2017-2-28 08:43","userId":"basertyu","userName":"小鸠世界第一可爱","userSign":"","message":"总感觉没听说过这回事啊<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">我是不是活在了错误的时代"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/10/1010.jpg","floor":"#2-2","id":"1216333","time":"2017-2-28 08:44","userId":"fireattack","userName":"烈之斩","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">basertyu(流氓豆)</span> 说: 总感觉没听说过这回事啊我是不是活在了错误的时代</q></div>我说的不太准确，应该说塚在<span style=\"text-decoration: line-through;\">现代</span>（划掉，搜了下好像很早以前就是当做异体字了）汉语里认为是冢的异体字"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/15/92/159245.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1216346","time":"2017-2-28 10:36","userId":"bogoo","userName":"波菇","userSign":"(漫畫是塑造每個人夢想的東西)","message":"【正字通】冢，俗作塚。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/16/52/165229.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1216347","time":"2017-2-28 11:15","userId":"kjl10","userName":"KSailorII","userSign":"(ドンドンドナッツ、デイデイアップ)","message":"你需要一份<a href=\"https://zh.wikisource.org/zh-hans/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E8%A7%84%E8%8C%83%E6%B1%89%E5%AD%97%E8%A1%A8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">通用规范汉字表</a>。<br><br>另外，日文新字体下的塚其实和汉字是有一点区别的。","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/20/25/202532.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1216366","time":"2017-2-28 14:29","userId":"buernia","userName":"奈白不弍","userSign":"(我追番少，你可别骗我。)","message":"在现行规范下，“塚” 是 “冢” 的异体字。在中文里应写为 “手冢治虫”。<br>中文不像日文那样会保留使用一个汉字的多种写法，日本人名在中文里应该进行必要的转换，异体字转为规范字，繁体字（在简体中文里）转为简化字。<br><br>不过在转换时需要注意一些汉字在两者之间的对应关系，如果不了解这些字的来龙去脉的话很容易弄错。参考：<a href=\"http://www.zhihu.com/question/44341331/answer/97227958\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">http://www.zhihu.com/question/44341331/answer/97227958</a>","sub":[]}]